Another Software By GoseTech! 


This Time a bot for World of Warcraft! 

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This bot is Undetectable & simple! The bot will:

1: Join Random Battlegrounds.
2: Leave finnished Battlegrounds.
3: Requeue.
4: Use ingame Scripts. Simply set an ingame Script to actionbar 1,2 or 3 & the software will use them frequently. 
5: Won't Go AFK.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This Bot is Created by GoseTech / Martin and it's an Open Beta! The software is open for exploration and for you to report bugs & sugesstions! 

This bot requires Internet to start, This is beacause the software is retreiving som information from my server(This to prevent Steaing of the software). 

If internet Access is not found. The bot Won't start.
